<ad href="../input_devices/index_mouse.html" title="The mouse:
    inherently injurious?">
  <img width="55" src="../photos/mouse.jpg" alt="Mouse"/>
  Imagine using a pen with a button on its side.  Such a
  button does not work too well; it entails a cramped and
  unhealthy grip.  In a more subtle way, conventional mouse
  design is as problematic.  A simple solution exists.
</ad>